Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:01:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:42.09,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Stella!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:45.85,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,She's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.48,0:01:50.84,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,She isn't as pale as she was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.84,0:01:52.51,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You must be dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.30,0:01:54.37,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.36,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,It's not dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.58,0:02:20.82,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:22.74,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.53,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,When did we last meet? At the graveyard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:30.12,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I could never forget you after \Nwhat you'd done to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.13,0:02:34.63,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:39.59,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You always cause me so much trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.01,0:02:43.04,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.00,0:02:46.74,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You accepted my deal, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.42,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.04,0:02:56.39,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Your curse is as powerful as mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:59.36,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cursed to live on forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:02.78,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You're cursed to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.68,0:03:07.82,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,So give me your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.79,0:03:15.29,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,It's my arm that you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:16.42,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.42,0:03:19.99,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,That part looks the most usable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:25.34,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a part of me in exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.91,0:03:29.88,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you'll have \Na body that can never die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.66,0:03:33.76,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I can't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.18,0:03:39.43,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying you have another option?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.05,0:03:41.90,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.75,0:03:48.41,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Do I just need to give you my arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.34,0:03:53.37,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,First, let's make sure my \Nbody doesn't reject it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.65,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.65,0:04:03.26,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Now it's your turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.10,0:04:08.01,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.01,0:04:10.69,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You might be freed from your curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:13.62,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:16.65,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You won't change into \Nanother form or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.54,0:04:19.13,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.64,0:04:24.78,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:29.54,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.19,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.63,0:04:35.85,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. I was just thinking\Nabout how I still hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.64,0:04:38.12,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:02.51,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.89,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Transplant complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.95,0:05:10.02,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you won't \Ndie just from bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:13.57,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't seem like my body's rejecting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.80,0:05:22.72,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyeball makes the world \Nlook bright and shiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.54,0:05:25.46,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I envy you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:35.11,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,We're the only people in this \Nworld who see what we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:41.76,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have your arm once \Nthe curse settles in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:46.41,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll all be \Ndone while you're asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.48,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to borrow the power \Nthat's left in your eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.68,0:05:52.46,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.11,0:05:57.66,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I told you. I hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:00.51,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:14.74,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.28,0:06:17.55,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:20.90,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:22.97,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,It's nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:26.70,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I know this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.63,0:06:29.54,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:35.91,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.36,0:06:38.54,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:41.20,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for watching the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:42.84,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't too scary, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.84,0:06:46.08,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Fumiki was with me, \Nso everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.08,0:06:47.34,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.97,0:06:51.01,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiki's lucky he takes after his dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.03,0:06:57.13,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,This is before my dad and \Nlittle brother vanished.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:59.20,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Fumiki's a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:03.43,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I can change his diaper now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:07.82,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.34,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.34,0:07:12.65,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're a good girl, too, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.72,0:07:17.56,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Mommy, Mommy, I want to help make dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.56,0:07:19.00,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.05,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What should I have you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:22.93,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:22.25,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.93,0:07:27.76,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,She used to have a really happy smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.97,0:07:39.00,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.00,0:07:39.68,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Just a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:42.04,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're gonna get wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.04,0:07:44.76,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.39,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're home late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.88,0:07:48.33,Magus-Flashback,,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:47.67,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.30,0:07:50.85,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:51.94,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.94,0:07:54.79,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I can't walk!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:56.53,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.08,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I took after my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.73,0:08:09.79,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Is work tough?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.79,0:08:12.76,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I have more night shifts now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.76,0:08:16.81,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. I wish I could work, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.81,0:08:19.66,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You already take care of things \Naround the house, Chika.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.06,0:08:22.64,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Chise's like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:23.76,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a frail body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.58,0:08:27.22,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better with you around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.74,0:08:29.52,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Yuuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:31.04,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Frail body...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.56,0:08:34.53,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Mom was the same as me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.07,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,This is my memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:25.29,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,He's keeping me in a dream \Nso that I don't wake up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.00,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Car—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.91,0:09:34.08,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.08,0:09:36.21,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.61,0:09:40.30,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fragment of him \Nthat's been chopped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:47.15,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,He's attached and assumed \Nall kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.15,0:09:52.78,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Which is the real him, what \Nhe even was to begin with...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.92,0:09:55.96,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,none of it is clear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.18,0:10:01.13,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he making me see \Nall this stuff from my past?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:03.57,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Probably to upset you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.80,0:10:09.18,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,That there is hurting you,\Nbut it's also protecting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.57,0:10:13.97,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,It's the reason you're able \Nto talk to something like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:17.25,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.94,0:10:21.03,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.06,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Not until you're ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.90,0:10:30.03,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.31,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay, I'll calm him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.64,0:10:38.15,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:03.40,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, are you going somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:07.37,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Chise, do you want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.84,0:11:11.08,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.08,0:11:12.20,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.39,0:11:19.31,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Well, good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:22.85,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Come back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:30.28,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Dad never...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.61,0:11:31.67,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.54,Magus-Internal/narrator,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,...came back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.99,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,That's all you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.09,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,That door won't open.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.44,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.82,0:11:56.04,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.65,0:11:57.92,Magus-Internal/narrator,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since this day...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.04,0:12:03.46,Magus-Flashback,Person A,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.46,0:12:05.07,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.61,0:12:07.94,Magus-Flashback,Person A,0000,0000,0000,,Something's odd lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:10.20,Magus-Flashback,Person B,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since Hatori-san showed up, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.57,0:12:12.58,Magus-Flashback,Thing,0000,0000,0000,,Want some help?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:18.59,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome h—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.47,0:12:24.96,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:30.55,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who said you can't be scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.58,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:35.63,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.40,0:12:41.58,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.60,0:12:44.84,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:47.46,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:00.64,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:04.44,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Help, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:14.44,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.44,0:13:15.27,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:33.74,Magus-Flashback,Person B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's midnight! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.87,0:13:36.11,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:38.02,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.41,0:13:39.99,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I have to be strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:46.72,Magus-Flashback,Thing A,0000,0000,0000,,That guy who was protecting\Nthem isn't around lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.72,0:13:49.69,Magus-Flashback,Thing B,0000,0000,0000,,Poor thing. He must have gotten sick of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.69,0:13:51.32,Magus-Flashback,Thing A,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:53.46,Magus-Flashback,Thing B,0000,0000,0000,,An abandoned daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:55.69,Magus-Flashback,Thing A,0000,0000,0000,,Pitiful and appetizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.94,0:14:12.40,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.97,0:14:14.32,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.83,0:14:15.59,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.17,0:14:17.55,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.21,0:14:21.67,sign_20601_165_Popular_job_list,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Popular job listings!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.61,0:14:26.23,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:29.85,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I have to protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:32.01,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.94,0:14:34.29,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.70,0:14:39.82,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be okay on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.30,0:14:41.39,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:45.36,Magus-Flashback,World's Worst Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It would be so much easier \Nfor me without her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.43,0:14:48.27,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy! That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.24,0:15:05.49,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But, if she weren't here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.60,0:15:31.93,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.60,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,have given birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:48.50,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have given birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.80,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,M... om...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.56,Magus-Flashback-internal,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What have I done?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.84,0:16:22.23,Magus-Flashback,Chhh,0000,0000,0000,,Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.24,0:16:27.01,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.00,0:16:29.21,Magus-Flashback,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.90,0:16:39.17,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,To upset me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.06,0:16:41.38,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,To {\i1}upset{\i0} me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:45.34,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}really{\i0} upsetting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:49.91,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:16:59.33,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have given birth to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.34,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.74,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,It's because your body is so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:07.60,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.69,0:17:09.05,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.76,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You should have died.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:17.31,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Die, die, die, die, \Ndie, die, die... Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.31,0:17:20.04,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you finish me off, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.37,0:17:25.32,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't my real mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.35,0:17:29.36,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,You're the mom that exists inside of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:34.82,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,The mom that I created\Nafter she strangled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.25,0:17:46.76,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I talked to Nevin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.15,0:17:52.37,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Angelica-san, Simon-san, Alice and Renfred,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:56.27,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Lindel-san, the people of the fairy world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.97,0:18:00.60,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Ruth, Silky, Stella,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.04,0:18:03.15,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Elias...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.22,0:18:07.67,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I got to meet all kinds of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:13.12,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Without them, I would have \Ndied before I'd met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.29,0:18:18.99,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.59,0:18:21.63,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Chise.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.54,0:18:24.09,Default,World's Best Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.86,0:18:29.03,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,You endured for my sake, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.28,0:18:35.14,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,You endured and endured, but in the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:43.20,Magus-Flashback-internal,Tree Dragon,0000,0000,0000,,You're free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.97,0:18:53.22,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.56,0:18:57.48,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I loved you, Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.31,0:19:01.13,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I have lots of happy memories with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.08,0:19:06.37,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, ever since that day,\N I couldn't remember any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.98,0:19:11.64,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,But thanks to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.13,0:19:16.42,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I met someone that I cared\Nfor even more than myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.39,0:19:21.94,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was strong, but he \Nturned out to be pretty troubled.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:26.24,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.39,0:19:29.40,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:33.02,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.35,0:19:42.54,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for letting go of me that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.33,0:19:48.03,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.17,0:19:52.90,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forget you yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.35,0:19:59.29,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm going to leave you and move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.34,0:20:23.98,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.58,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.94,0:20:31.88,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,I'm what keeps one living on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.71,0:20:36.28,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,The curse and blessing that \Nwas given for his sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.80,0:20:37.88,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.54,0:20:39.91,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Cartaphilus?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.21,0:20:46.17,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,They planted me in you, and \Nyou're trying to accept me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.57,0:20:52.49,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,So as long as you wish to \Nlive, I'll be your blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.36,0:20:59.48,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Even if that means tearing at what consumes \Nand protects you for all eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.71,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What do... What do you desire?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.22,0:21:05.15,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:06.59,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What's the price?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:10.00,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,What you say sounds good only for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.63,0:21:16.54,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,There's one wish that I've heard many times.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.33,0:21:22.29,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Can you grant that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.24,0:21:28.81,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's starting to set in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.00,0:21:31.54,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,How vile.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.46,0:21:34.10,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.38,0:21:40.35,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're awake—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.35,0:21:43.32,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to do things the way you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.48,0:21:47.29,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can grant you your wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:52.78,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,But I can hear you out, \Nand try to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.41,0:21:58.51,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,"Help me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.22,0:22:04.75,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,For centuries, for millennia,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.57,0:22:09.22,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,they've been shouting, "Help me."
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.18,0:22:15.87,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know why you desire this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.23,0:22:19.97,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Why, when you think as you \Ndo, you still do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.97,0:22:21.44,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Why you've done this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.12,0:22:24.02,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.94,0:23:59.01,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,The girl tries to make \Nsense of Joseph's truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.01,0:24:05.33,Default,CHHH,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, the mage, having lost the girl, \Nloses his human form, and is forced to wander.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:06.54,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You saw?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.78,0:24:07.85,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,You saw me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.85,0:24:09.34,Default,Wizard of Omg,0000,0000,0000,,My past?
